@startuml spec-lifecycle
title LiveSpec Core — Spec Lifecycle
skinparam defaultFontName Helvetica
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam BackgroundColor white
skinparam ArrowColor #111
skinparam ArrowFontColor #111
skinparam rectangle {
  BorderColor #111
  BackgroundColor white
  FontColor #111
}
skinparam database {
  BorderColor #111
  BackgroundColor white
  FontColor #111
}
skinparam usecase {
  BorderColor #111
  BackgroundColor white
  FontColor #111
}
skinparam card {
  BorderColor #111
  BackgroundColor white
  FontColor #111
}
skinparam actor {
  BorderColor #111
  BackgroundColor white
  FontColor #111
}

actor "Human\nuser" as HumanUser
actor "Agent" as Agent #LightSkyBlue

rectangle "Initial seed\nof intent" as SeedIntent #FFFFFF;line.dashed
card "/livespec:seed" as SeedCmd #LightYellow

database "SPECIFICATION/\n(spec.md, contracts.md,\nconstraints.md, scenarios.md,\nnon-functional-requirements.md)" as Spec
database "history/vNNN/\nsnapshots" as History
database "proposed_changes/\n(pending)" as Proposed

rectangle "Observation\n(spec-internal:\nambiguity, contradiction,\nundefined term)" as SpecObs #FFFFFF;line.dashed

card "/livespec:critique" as CritiqueCmd #LightYellow
note right of CritiqueCmd : Role: surface observations\nbased on observing the\nspec. NOT the implementation.\nFinds spec-internal issues\n(ambiguity, contradiction,\ndangling refs).

card "/livespec:propose-changes\n(formal or quick-deposit)" as ProposeCmd #LightYellow
card "/livespec:revise\n(selective per proposal)" as ReviseCmd #LightYellow

usecase "Revision\nneeded?" as RevisionNeeded
card "/livespec:doctor" as DoctorCmd #LightYellow
card "/livespec:prune-history" as PruneCmd #LightYellow
card "/livespec:help" as HelpCmd #LightYellow

HumanUser --> SeedIntent
HumanUser --> SeedCmd : invokes
Agent --> SeedCmd : drives
SeedIntent --> SeedCmd
SeedCmd --> Spec : authors initial tree
SeedCmd --> History : writes v001

Spec --> SpecObs
SpecObs --> CritiqueCmd : analyzed by
CritiqueCmd --> Proposed : drafts findings\nas proposed changes

HumanUser --> RevisionNeeded
RevisionNeeded -right-> ProposeCmd : YES (user intent)
ProposeCmd --> Proposed : writes
Proposed --> ReviseCmd : consumed by
HumanUser --> ReviseCmd : per-proposal\nconfirm
ReviseCmd --> Spec : mutates
ReviseCmd --> History : cuts new vNNN

DoctorCmd ..> Spec : static + LLM-driven\ninvariants
DoctorCmd ..> Proposed : hygiene
DoctorCmd ..> History : structural checks

History --> PruneCmd : oldest collapsed
PruneCmd --> History : pruned-marker

note bottom of Spec : Mutated ONLY through\n/livespec:propose-changes →\n/livespec:revise. Direct edits forbidden\nafter v001 seed.

note right of ReviseCmd : Selective per-proposal\naccept / modify / reject.\nEach revise pass cuts\nexactly one new vNNN.

@enduml
